description:
In this insightful episode of Money Mindset, ace investor Vijay Kedia shares his remarkable journey, investment strategies, and lessons from decades of market experience. From the early days of building his portfolio to navigating bear markets and spotting future trends, this conversation is a must-watch for every investor. Vijay Kedia dives deep into his SMILE framework, discusses conviction during corrections, case studies like Cera Sanitaryware and Tejas Networks, and even touches on alternative investments like crypto and Chinese ETFs.
Chapters:
00:00 - Introduction
1:15 - Early Age and Investment Journey
5:30 - Investing Tips and SMILE Framework
9:45 - Bear Market Psychology
15:35 - How to Maintain Conviction During Market Corrections
19:10 - Cera Sanitaryware Case Study
22:40 - Market Trends in the Next 5-10 Years
32:20 - Cultivating Risk Appetite: Vijay Kedia’s Approach
45:03 - Skillsets and Formulas for Successful Investing
53:02 - 90-Hour Work Week: Vijay Kedia’s Experience
56:03 - Investing in Chinese ETFs: Insights
1:04:00 - Alternative Investments: Crypto Discussion
1:05:00 - Vijay Kedia’s Biggest Win and Loss in the Market
1:11:20 - Tejas Networks Case Study
1:15:20 - Identifying Market Leaders Across Sectors
